{
  "page": "Jessamyn Redfort",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redfort\" title=\"House Redfort\"><img alt=\"House Redfort.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/73/House_Redfort.svg/50px-House_Redfort.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/73/House_Redfort.svg/75px-House_Redfort.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/73/House_Redfort.svg/100px-House_Redfort.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Jessamyn Redfort</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redfort\" title=\"House Redfort\"><img alt=\"House Redfort.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/73/House_Redfort.svg/50px-House_Redfort.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/73/House_Redfort.svg/75px-House_Redfort.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/73/House_Redfort.svg/100px-House_Redfort.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Jessamyn_Redfort_by_dreamgirlindescansos.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Jessamyn Redfort by dreamgirlindescansos.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/53/Jessamyn_Redfort_by_dreamgirlindescansos.jpg/350px-Jessamyn_Redfort_by_dreamgirlindescansos.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"560\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/53/Jessamyn_Redfort_by_dreamgirlindescansos.jpg/524px-Jessamyn_Redfort_by_dreamgirlindescansos.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/53/Jessamyn_Redfort_by_dreamgirlindescansos.jpg/699px-Jessamyn_Redfort_by_dreamgirlindescansos.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Jessamyn by dreamgirlindescansos</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Redfort\" title=\"House Redfort\">House Redfort</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Arryn\" title=\"Jeyne Arryn\">Jeyne Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jessamyn Redfort</b> was a noblewoman from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Redfort\" title=\"House Redfort\">House Redfort</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jessamyn_Redfort&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Jessamyn was a \"dear companion\" of <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Arryn\" title=\"Jeyne Arryn\">Jeyne Arryn</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Eyrie\" title=\"Lord of the Eyrie\">Lady of the Eyrie</a>. Jeyne, who never married, died in Jessamyn's arms at the <a href=\"/index.php/Motherhouse_of_Maris\" title=\"Motherhouse of Maris\">Motherhouse of Maris</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/134_AC\" title=\"134 AC\">134&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Jessamyn\">Quotes about Jessamyn</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jessamyn_Redfort&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Jessamyn\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Forty years of age, [Jeyne Arryn] perished in the <a href=\"/index.php/Motherhouse_of_Maris\" title=\"Motherhouse of Maris\">Motherhouse of Maris</a> on its stony island in the harbor of <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a>, wrapped in the arms of Jessamyn Redfort, her \"dear companion.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a> writing in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood,_Being_a_History_of_the_Targaryen_Kings_of_Westeros\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood, Being a History of the Targaryen Kings of Westeros\">Fire &amp; Blood, Being a History of the Targaryen Kings of Westeros</a></i></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jessamyn_Redfort&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Lysene Spring and the End of Regency.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404162558\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.098 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.347 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 684/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10589/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6670/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1509/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1454/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.230/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  336.022      1 -total\n 94.89%  318.851      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 94.39%  317.166      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.60%   32.263     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.28%   14.384      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.49%    8.361      3 Template:Ref\n  1.65%    5.531      1 Template:Date\n  1.60%    5.373      3 Template:Ref/core\n  0.77% 